{"tid":1847672,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港人參與遊行後被拒入境　一度與內地妻子分離","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T09:53:39.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6446dd35225d53fb41bdd98911060759790d52","tid":1847672,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"有港人參與遊行後，被內地以危害國家安全為由拒絕他入境，他不敢再在香港參與示威活動或發表政見，新年亦擔心未能與內地的太太團聚。<br />\n<br />\n太太在內地的鄧先生每星期都會經關口上深圳至少一次探家人，但12月參加過一次在屯門的示威後，翌日就過不了關。<br />\n<br />\n被拒入境的前一日，他曾參與「光復屯門公園」行動，他相信這是不能入境的主因。<br />\n<br />\n為了與家人團聚，他打算再闖關，他想到一個方法。換證後他亦試過成功過關，但他相信往後不會每次順利，又估計自己已被列入內地的黑名單，感到無奈。<br />\n<br />\n鄧生稱自己並非社運人士，尚且被內地「關注」，他已經尋求立法會議員的協助，希望港府嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=378336&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378336%26hot%3D1&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=13500bed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378336%26hot%3D1&h=79f133d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=378336&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"12e6721a435e2da6cd8ef5ed9fb64c9bb7ddd0ba","tid":1847672,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"大陸妻子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81890ba086ecd6b1f6740017b0aca08c51db7a42","tid":1847672,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:02:58.000Z","msg":"被支那閪統戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3040b8ae54f005e3ba5d5a0d8fe820b4de2b8e2","tid":1847672,"uid":250622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e6721a435e2da6cd8ef5ed9fb64c9bb7ddd0ba","tid":1847672,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"大陸妻子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 